# Configuration file for zathura, for bépo keyboard
# (It seems to only works if the config is in /etc/zathurarc)
#
# Maintainer: sheoak
# Version:    O.11

# Basic bépo keyboard configuration for zathura
map [normal]     s scroll up
map [normal]     t scroll down
map [normal]     c scroll left
map [normal]     r scroll right

# s is used
map [fullscreen] w adjust_window width

#map [normal]    <C-o> navigate previous
#map [normal]    <C-p> navigate next

map [normal]     <C-s> scroll half-up
map [normal]     <C-t> scroll half-down
map [normal]     <C-c> rotate rotate-ccw
map [normal]     <C-r> rotate rotate-cw

map [normal]     <BackSpace>   scroll full-up
map [normal]     <Return>      scroll full-down

map [normal]     w zoom to width
map [normal]     h reload
#map [normal]     H reload the document



